name.jp: ブルーファントキャット

description.en: Who yearns for a sidekick when you've got a spellbinding feline? A bewitched cat as your mystical accomplice, always ready for ghostly incantations!

description.cns: 拥有一只迷人的猫后，谁还需要其他同伴呢？作为你的神秘帮手，这只被施了魔法的猫随时准备好施放幻影咒语！
